          "lines": [
            "I heard you were coming! I'm glad to have another set of eyes round here.",
            "I'd recommend finding supplies and learning how to kill the undead.  It's just going to get worst.",
            "You can also use my work bench to start crafting useful items.  Go look for resources to train some professions.",
            "Also checkout my shop as I've been making some things you may want, but it'll cost you."
          ],
          "completeQuestId": "quest_1776310554860"
        },
