    {
      "row": 84,
      "col": 143,
      "dialogueSessions": [
        {
          "when": {
            "type": "always"
          },
          "lines": [
            "Please, you have to help me find my daughter.",
            "She was right behind me holding my hand, but something must have grabbed her.",
            "I know she is still in the forest, you have to help me find here.  Take my shotgun, I'm sure it'll help you in their."
          ],
          "grantQuestId": "quest_1775977610190"
        },
        {
          "when": {
            "type": "all",
            "conditions": [
              {
                "type": "quest_active_final_talk_turn_in",
                "questId": "quest_1775977610190"
              }
            ]
          },
          "lines": [
            "Oh that stubborn girl! I should have known she wouldn't go with a stranger.",
            "At least I know exactly how to get to her. Thank you kind stranger."
          ],
          "completeQuestId": "quest_1775977610190"
        },
