            "type": "all",
            "conditions": [
              {
                "type": "quest_not_active",
                "questId": "quest_1776310554860"
              }
            ]
          },
          "lines": [
            "If I were you, I'd try to make it out of this area.  Every day they grow in numbers.",
            "Go find my neighbor Ollie is to the north west.  I've been talking to him over the radio and he says his encampment is safe.",
            "Farewell and good luck."
          ],
          "grantQuestId": "quest_1776310554860"
        },
        {
          "when": {
            "type": "all",
            "conditions": [
              {
                "type": "quest_active",
                "questId": "quest_1776310554860"
              }
            ]
          },
          "lines": [
            "Go on, Ollie is waiting for you!"
          ]
        },
        {
          "when": {
            "type": "always"
          },
          "lines": [
